OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FChance of a
OL,6,Ffew showers this evening. Then the
OL,7,Frest of the night will be dry and cold
OL,8,Fwith clear periods and a slight frost.
OL,9,FNortherly breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FMost of the day will be dry
OL,12,Fwith some hazy sunshine in the
OL,13,Fmorning. Outbreaks of rain will spread
OL,14,Feast in the evening. Light winds at
OL,15,Ffirst, strengthening later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
